highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Jaipur. “Kesariya” is the highest at #1.
“Rasiya” by Pritam, Shreya Ghoshal, and TUSHAR JOSHI is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Jaipur, up 67 spots at #21.
“Tu Aake Dekhle” by King has been on Top Songs Jaipur the longest, at 51 weeks straight.
“Chogada (From "Loveyatri")” by Darshan Raval, Asees Kaur, and Lijo George-Dj Chetas is the highest new entry on Top Songs Jaipur at #85.
